      <title>亿万富翁ong的新加坡认罪延迟了医生报告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/billionaire-ong-s-singapore-guilty-plea-delayed-on-doctor-report</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁Ong Beng Seng将在以后的日期内认罪，这比与前新加坡政府部长有关的案件最初预期的，该案件因从财产大亨那里获得礼物而被判入狱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/billionaire-ong-s-singapore-guilty-plea-delayed-on-doctor-report</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 03:28:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Thaksin审查后，泰国总理在不信任的情况下幸存下来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/thai-pm-survives-first-no-confidence-vote-after-thaksin-scrutiny</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在为期两天的辩论之后，泰国总理佩顿顿·辛瓦瓦特拉（Paetongtarn Shinawatra）在议会中幸免于难，反对派针对她父亲所谓的对政府的影响及其对经济管理不善的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/thai-pm-survives-first-no-confidence-vote-after-thaksin-scrutiny</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 03:14:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德拉希称德国对国防支出的转变为“改变游戏规则”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/draghi-calls-germany-s-shift-on-defense-spending-game-changer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前欧洲中央银行总裁马里奥·德拉吉（Mario Draghi）表示，德国提高国防支出的决定是“改变游戏规则的人”，但警告说，在实施方式方面存在风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/draghi-calls-germany-s-shift-on-defense-spending-game-changer</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 02:10:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>CK和Hutchison说，在中国愤怒的情况下继续进行港口交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/ck-hutchison-is-said-to-proceed-with-port-deal-despite-china-ire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[熟悉此事的人们说，CK Hutchison Holdings Ltd.计划将两个巴拿马港口出售给Blackrock Inc.领导的集团正按计划前进。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/ck-hutchison-is-said-to-proceed-with-port-deal-despite-china-ire</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 02:06:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国影响者被迫离开台湾支持入侵</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/china-influencer-forced-to-leave-taiwan-for-supporting-invasion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[面对台湾驱逐出境的中国有影响力的人因支持军事夺取的自我运营民主而被驱逐回到她的国家＆Mdash;随着台北加紧努力来反击北京的宣传。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/china-influencer-forced-to-leave-taiwan-for-supporting-invasion</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 01:57:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普可能会在数周内实施铜进口关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/trump-may-implement-copper-import-tariffs-within-weeks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据熟悉此事的人们说，美国对铜进口的关税可能会在几周内，比判决的截止日期提前几个月。在纽约交易的铜升至纪录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/trump-may-implement-copper-import-tariffs-within-weeks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 01:06:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>共和党更靠近减税计划，眼睛债务上限协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/republicans-move-closer-to-tax-cut-plan-eye-debt-ceiling-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党领导人说，他们正在就一项计划，以通过唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的2017年减税和增加债务上限的计划达成共识，因为国会希望在5月底批准经济方案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/republicans-move-closer-to-tax-cut-plan-eye-debt-ceiling-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 21:51:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃尔多安仔细踩踏以平息抗议和平静的市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/erdogan-treads-carefully-to-quell-protests-and-calm-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其总统雷切普·塔伊普·埃尔多安（Recep Tayyip Erdogan）正在采取措施，以确保全国各地的抗议活动不会恶化并在金融市场中遏制溃败，即使他把螺丝钉戴上对手。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/erdogan-treads-carefully-to-quell-protests-and-calm-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 17:10:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国说，即使俄罗斯列出条款，黑海休战也同意了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/us-says-russia-ukraine-agree-ceasefire-in-black-sea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国表示，俄罗斯和乌克兰同意在黑海停火，尽管克里姆林宫表示，其参与将取决于一系列先决条件，包括制裁救济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/us-says-russia-ukraine-agree-ceasefire-in-black-sea</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 11:07:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国顾问敦促到2035年将消费量提高到GDP的70％</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/china-adviser-urges-boosting-consumption-to-70-of-gdp-by-2035</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位政府顾问说，中国应将消费量提高到接近发达国家的水平，这是一名政府顾问说，这加剧了重新平衡世界第二大经济体的呼吁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/china-adviser-urges-boosting-consumption-to-70-of-gdp-by-2035</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 10:27:11 GMT</pubDate>
